`_sanitize_name`, `_ensure_namespace`, `_create_deployment`, `_create_service`, `wait_for_deployment_ready`, `deploy_agent`, `get_agent_status`, `delete_agent`\n- [ ] `AgentCubeProvider` class with `__init__`, `_sanitize_name`, `_ensure_namespace`, `deploy_agent_runtime`, `get_agent_runtime`\n- [ ] AgentRuntime CR body template with correct spec structure\n- [ ] `DockerService` enhanced with `push_image`, `tag_image`, `login`, `get_local_image_url`\n- [ ] `PublishRuntime` class with `__init__`, `publish`, `_prepare_image_for_publishing`, `_prepare_local_image`, `_prepare_cloud_image`, `_publish_cr_to_k8s`, `_publish_k8s`, `_update_publish_metadata`\n- [ ] Provider validation: invalid provider raises `ValueError`\n- [ ] `publish` Typer command with all options: `--workspace`, `--version`, `--image-url`, `--image-username`, `--image-password`, `--description`, `--region`, `--cloud-provider`, `--provider`, `--node-port`, `--replicas`, `--namespace`, `--verbose`\n- [ ] Rich Progress spinner during publish\n- [ ] Success output: agent name, ID, endpoint, deployment type, namespace\n- [ ] Error handling via `_handle_error()`\n- [ ] Error recorded in metadata before exception\n- [ ] NodePort validation (30000-32767 range)\n- [ ] Required field validation: `router_url`, `workload_manager_url` for agentcube provider\n- [ ] `image_url` required for local build mode\n- [ ] Unit tests for KubernetesProvider (init, sanitize, deploy, wait, status, delete)\n- [ ] Unit tests for AgentCubeProvider (init, deploy, patch, get)\n- [ ] Unit tests for PublishRuntime (publish, prepare image, metadata update)\n- [ ] Unit tests for DockerService publish methods\n- [ ] Unit tests for CLI command\n- [ ] Integration tests for publish workflow\n- [ ] `kubernetes>=28.0.0` dependency added\n- [ ] All providers exported from `services/__init__.py`\n- [ ] `PublishRuntime` exported from `runtime/__init__.py`\n- [ ] All tests pass with >80% coverage\n- [ ] Ruff lint passes\n- [ ] MyPy type check passes\n\n---\n\n## File Changes Summary\n\n| File | Action | Lines Changed | Description |\n|------|--------|---------------|-------------|\n| `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` | Modify | ~20 | Add `k8s_deployment`, `agent_id`, `readiness_probe_path`, `readiness_probe_port` fields |\n| `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py` | Create | ~150 | `KubernetesProvider` class for standard Deployment/Service |\n| `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py` | Create | ~100 | `AgentCubeProvider` class for AgentRuntime CR |\n| `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/docker_service.py` | Modify | ~40 | Add `tag_image`, `login`, `get_local_image_url`, enhance `push_image` |\n| `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/__init__.py` | Modify | ~5 | Export `KubernetesProvider`, `AgentCubeProvider` |\n| `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py` | Create | ~180 | `PublishRuntime` class with publish orchestration |\n| `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/__init__.py` | Modify | ~5 | Export `PublishRuntime` |\n| `cmd/cli/agentcube/cli/main.py` | Modify | ~60 | Add `publish` command with Typer options |\n| `cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py` | Create | ~200 | Unit tests for KubernetesProvider |\n| `cmd/cli/tests/test_agentcube_provider.py` | Create | ~150 | Unit tests for AgentCubeProvider |\n| `cmd/cli/tests/test_publish_runtime.py` | Create | ~250 | Unit tests for PublishRuntime |\n| `cmd/cli/tests/test_docker_service.py` | Modify | ~80 | Unit tests for DockerService publish methods |\n| `cmd/cli/tests/test_publish_cli.py` | Create | ~100 | Unit tests for CLI publish command |\n| `cmd/cli/tests/test_publish_integration.py` | Create | ~120 | Integration tests for publish workflow |\n| `cmd/cli/pyproject.toml` | Modify | ~10 | Add `kubernetes>=28.0.0` dependency |\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Notes\n\n- **Design completed at Stage ST-3**\n- **Reference implementation**: `BuildRuntime` in `build_runtime.py` provides similar pattern\n- **Provider pattern**: Two providers with similar structure, validate required fields differently\n- **AgentRuntime CR**: Custom Resource from Volcano AgentCube project\n- **Name sanitization**: DNS-compliant, lowercase, max 63 chars, replace special chars with `-`\n- **NodePort range**: 30000-32767 (Kubernetes standard range)\n- **Deployment timeout**: 120 seconds default, poll every 2 seconds\n- **Rich Progress**: Use `SpinnerColumn` + `TextColumn` for publish spinner\n- **Error recording**: Always record error in metadata before raising exception\n- **Option overrides**: CLI options override metadata fields\n- **Image preparation**: Different path for local vs cloud build mode\n- **CR patch on conflict**: If AgentRuntime CR exists, patch instead of create (handle 409)\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Timeline\n\n| Phase | Tasks | Status | Completion |\n|-------|-------|--------|------------|\n| Phase 1: Metadata Model Extensions | T1.1-T1.3 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 2: KubernetesProvider Class | T2.1-T2.10 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 3: AgentCubeProvider Class | T3.1-T3.7 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 4: DockerService Enhancements | T4.1-T4.4 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 5: PublishRuntime Class | T5.1-T5.11 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 6: CLI Command Implementation | T6.1-T6.2 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 7: Unit Tests - KubernetesProvider | T7.1-T7.10 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 8: Unit Tests - AgentCubeProvider | T8.1-T8.8 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 9: Unit Tests - PublishRuntime | T9.1-T9.13 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 10: Unit Tests - DockerService | T10.1-T10.5 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 11: Unit Tests - CLI Command | T11.1-T11.4 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 12: Integration Tests | T12.1-T12.5 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 13: Dependencies & Validation | T13.1-T13.6 | Pending | 0% |\n\n**Total Progress: 0% Complete (0/77 tasks)**"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/cmd/cli/agentcube/cli/main.py":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v